title: Guides: Medical Students Resource Guide: Home
author: C Scott Dorris
description: A library resource guide for students in Georgetown University's School of Medicine.
cleaned_text: Welcome to Dahlgren Memorial Library's Guide to Resources for students in the School of Medicine. The purpose of this guide is to help you navigate through the many resources available to you through the Dahlgren Memorial Library (DML) system and freely available online. If you have any suggestions for additional applicable resources, please tell your liaison through contact information listed on the right. Also, feel free to contact your liaison with any questions regarding resources or research.
